{{#base headerTitle="Welcome to {{appName}}!" headerSubtitle="Your journey to business transformation starts now"}}

<div class="greeting">
    🎉 Welcome {{firstName}}!
</div>

<div class="message">
    <p><strong>Congratulations!</strong> You've just taken a transformative step for your business by joining {{appName}} - Africa's premier business management platform.</p>
    
    <p>We're thrilled to have you aboard! Your account has been successfully created and you now have access to powerful tools designed specifically for African businesses like yours.</p>
</div>

<div class="success-notice">
    <p>✅ <strong>Account Successfully Created!</strong> You can now log in and start exploring all the features {{appName}} has to offer.</p>
</div>

<div class="cta-section">
    <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="cta-button">Access Your Dashboard</a>
</div>

<div class="info-card">
    <h3>🚀 Your {{appName}} Business Suite</h3>
    <p>Here's what you now have access to:</p>
    
    <div class="detail-grid">
        <div class="detail-item">
            <span class="detail-label">📈 CRM & Leads</span>
            <span class="detail-value">Manage customers, track leads, and grow your sales pipeline</span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-item">
            <span class="detail-label">📋 Task Management</span>
            <span class="detail-value">Organize projects, assign tasks, and track team productivity</span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-item">
            <span class="detail-label">📊 Analytics & Reports</span>
            <span class="detail-value">Data-driven insights to make smarter business decisions</span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-item">
            <span class="detail-label">📱 Mobile Access</span>
            <span class="detail-value">Manage your business on-the-go with our mobile app</span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-item">
            <span class="detail-label">🏪 Inventory Control</span>
            <span class="detail-value">Track stock levels, manage suppliers, and optimize inventory</span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-item">
            <span class="detail-label">💰 Financial Tracking</span>
            <span class="detail-value">Monitor cash flow, generate invoices, and track expenses</span>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="info-card">
    <h4>⚡ Quick Start Guide</h4>
    <ul class="feature-list">
        <li><strong>Complete Your Profile:</strong> Add business details and logo for personalization</li>
        <li><strong>Import Your Data:</strong> Upload existing contacts, products, and inventory</li>
        <li><strong>Invite Your Team:</strong> Add team members and set up user permissions</li>
        <li><strong>Customize Dashboard:</strong> Arrange widgets to match your workflow</li>
        <li><strong>Set Up Notifications:</strong> Configure alerts for important business events</li>
        <li><strong>Explore Mobile App:</strong> Download {{appName}} mobile for iOS and Android</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="message">
    <p><strong>Your Account Details:</strong></p>
</div>

<div class="info-card">
    <h4>📋 Account Information</h4>
    <div class="detail-grid">
        <div class="detail-item">
            <span class="detail-label">Account Type</span>
            <span class="detail-value">{{planName}} Plan</span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-item">
            <span class="detail-label">User ID</span>
            <span class="detail-value">{{userId}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-item">
            <span class="detail-label">Registration Date</span>
            <span class="detail-value">{{registrationDate}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-item">
            <span class="detail-label">Primary Email</span>
            <span class="detail-value">{{email}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-item">
            <span class="detail-label">Time Zone</span>
            <span class="detail-value">{{timeZone}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-item">
            <span class="detail-label">Organization</span>
            <span class="detail-value">{{organizationName}}</span>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="info-card">
    <h4>🎓 Learning Resources</h4>
    <p>Get the most out of {{appName}} with these helpful resources:</p>
    <ul class="feature-list">
        <li><strong>Video Tutorials:</strong> Step-by-step guides for every feature</li>
        <li><strong>Knowledge Base:</strong> Comprehensive documentation and FAQs</li>
        <li><strong>Webinar Training:</strong> Live training sessions with our experts</li>
        <li><strong>Community Forum:</strong> Connect with other {{appName}} users</li>
        <li><strong>24/7 Support:</strong> Get help whenever you need it</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="cta-section">
    <p style="margin-bottom: 15px; font-weight: 600;">Ready to transform your business?</p>
    <a href="{{onboardingUrl}}" class="cta-button">Start Onboarding Tour</a>
</div>

<div class="info-card">
    <h4>📞 Need Help Getting Started?</h4>
    <p>Our customer success team is here to ensure you get the most out of {{appName}}:</p>
    <div class="detail-grid">
        <div class="detail-item">
            <span class="detail-label">Email Support</span>
            <span class="detail-value">{{supportEmail}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-item">
            <span class="detail-label">Phone Support</span>
            <span class="detail-value">{{supportPhone}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-item">
            <span class="detail-label">Live Chat</span>
            <span class="detail-value">Available in your dashboard</span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-item">
            <span class="detail-label">Office Hours</span>
            <span class="detail-value">Mon-Fri, 8AM-6PM CAT</span>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="message">
    <p><strong>What makes {{appName}} special for African businesses?</strong></p>
    <p>We understand the unique challenges and opportunities in African markets. {{appName}} is built with local insights, supports multiple currencies, includes region-specific compliance features, and offers training in local languages.</p>
</div>

<div class="success-notice">
    <p>🌟 <strong>Special Welcome Offer:</strong> As a new user, you get 30 days of premium features absolutely free! Explore everything {{appName}} has to offer risk-free.</p>
</div>

<div class="message">
    <p>Thank you for choosing {{appName}}. We're excited to be part of your business success story!</p>
    
    <p><em>Best regards,<br>
    The {{appName}} Team 🚀</em></p>
</div>

{{/base}} 